{"tid":473472,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"北歐追光之旅 唔侵iPhone玩","createTime":"2017-11-19T09:19:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-19T15:25:23.000Z","uid":81135,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"bd275da2d1d713d70aec68495927283cd5de184f","tid":473472,"uid":81135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T09:19:58.000Z","msg":"小弟黎緊會去北歐<br />\n唔係專業人士 但唔想靠iphone嘥左啲靚景<br />\n所以想入手部相機（平平地$5000樓下）<br />\n已經做過research<br />\n主要想要大光圈F1.8高ISO同有得變焦<br />\n同埋儘量可以反鏡（但呢個唔係重點）<br />\n已經有幾部符合條件<br />\n但想聽下咁多位清既意見<br />\n<br />\n1. OM-D E-M10 Mark II DZK<br />\n呢部各樣都好好 但冇得反鏡 同埋去旅行唔知算唔算大<br />\n2. PowerShot G7 X Mark II<br />\n呢部見佢連星空都影到 極光應該都輕鬆<br />\n3. LUMIX DMC-LX10<br />\n呢部就上網見人地推薦 但小弟覺得細機黎講有少少貴<br />\n<br />\n小弟比較喜歡Canon果部 但又覺得Olympus有得換鏡幾型<br />\n<br />\n有其他建議又係筆直之內既機都想睇睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5955a96d22991f676af1312d7ccd91bd0f693a0","tid":473472,"uid":523,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T09:34:29.000Z","msg":"1. m43 片幅 亦都係三部入面片幅最大<br />\n但你嘅1.8大光圈要用邊支鏡？<br />\n<br />\n2,3. 隨身dc機 兩部差唔多<br />\n<br />\n個人建議 :sony a6000 kit set + samyang 12mm f2<br />\n加埋哂大約6000蚊  但apsc 片幅<br />\n支12mm f2 影極光出黎嘅效果同上面三部完全無得比"},{"pid":"481fe7c5c3a567ce3976dadf2f1661d167d18914","tid":473472,"uid":58116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T12:46:59.000Z","msg":"一支穩固嘅腳架加是但一部單反加支kit都影到，無反就算數，好快冇電。<br />\n識用m mode同手動對焦就得"},{"pid":"6c26f742d3cf237a5cdd1069876e747e6708e5cb","tid":473472,"uid":59408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T13:03:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一支穩固嘅腳架加是但一部單反加支kit都影到，無反就算數，好快冇電。<br />\n識用m mode同手動對焦就得</blockquote><br />\n冇錯， 零下廿度，舊電打七折<br />\n仲要帶厚手套保溫，㩒唔到無反啲掣，太細<br />\n<br />\n我個人都鐘意無反輕巧，<br />\n但呢個場合單反贏曬，<br />\n用電少，掣夠大"},{"pid":"4ed7b15adbc01f0349d08d250269595ea90c2880","tid":473472,"uid":123587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T13:04:05.000Z","msg":"正常強度極光F2.8或以下+高ISO+曝10秒以上配合就影到，但你機仔高ISO時noise高死梗，如果拍片iso要4000以上先錄到。重有焦距要有10-18mm，<br />\n如果你join D tour ($1000左右 1位) 去D暗D地方追光而果晚有大爆發，基上是但一部照機iphone都影到。"},{"pid":"290085af55c8cad833a7b92c7d6ad553d8f5d75b","tid":473472,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T13:11:56.000Z","msg":"點都買無反啦，普通dc仔真係麻麻地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 基本上事旦一部無反，加支24mm (35mm 等效) 以下嘅鏡都夠做，最重要留啲錢買腳架，買機送嗰啲真係唔掂，買枝$500-700應該夠做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed4f27ca9146019f9625e44b1289b8fcd45b25f1","tid":473472,"uid":34222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T13:17:32.000Z","msg":"用緊sony a6000 加支腳架夠唔夠做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5c64eec388020fdf111a9f6a4a4f78cb97370e3","tid":473472,"uid":143582,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T13:24:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用緊sony a6000 加支腳架夠唔夠做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n影到啦，你要擔心係舊電頂唔住"},{"pid":"b355b172fdce4e2d5e283c9fe6b165043b2a6ac6","tid":473472,"uid":123587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T15:14:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點都買無反啦，普通dc仔真係麻麻地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 基本上事旦一部無反，加支24mm (35mm 等效) 以下嘅鏡都夠做，最重要留啲錢買腳架，買機送嗰啲真係唔掂，買枝$500-700應該夠做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n$500-700肯定唔夠<br />\nD風大到好似10號風球咁"},{"pid":"ebadd413c732adfe9e8997c8be41fc20ccc4c4df","tid":473472,"uid":123587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T15:16:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用緊sony a6000 加支腳架夠唔夠做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我用A7<br />\n個mon凍到唔著"},{"pid":"11c40a4b0e9c1a172535d409159018962745a60c","tid":473472,"uid":14370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T15:25:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用緊sony a6000 加支腳架夠唔夠做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n岩岩去完 a6000 完全無問題 （負6度左右）"}]}